1. *Hoda* se ulicom. (He was walking down the street.)
2. Počela je da *hoda*. (She started to walk.)
3. Ona često *hoda* u park. (She often walks in the park.)
4. Rekao sam da *hodam* kući. (I said I'm walking home.)
5. *Hodali* smo ulicom. (We were walking down the street.)
6. *Hodao* sam tuda često. (I used to walk there often.)
7. *Hodamo* polako. (We are walking slowly.)
8. Ona *hoda* u školu. (She walks to school.)